{"tid":809641,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(做問卷，收$50)英文證書考試網上問卷","createTime":"2018-09-07T10:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T23:11:21.000Z","uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"61db92a5257db77190bba43427e1e2b753f045fd","tid":809641,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:29:22.000Z","msg":"英文證書考試網上問卷邀約(20分鐘/車馬費HKD50)<br />\n<br />\n在過去12個月參加過, 或者打算未來12個月參加以下考試:<br />\n<br />\n1- TOEFL託福考試;<br />\n2- PTE考試<br />\n.<br />\n附注:<br />\n1-滿17嵗以上香港居民,包括學生, 已經工作的人(為移民目的,工作目的,留學目的而參加英語考試).<br />\n2-已完成問卷的朋友請忽略.<br />\n<br />\n報名格式:<br />\n<br />\n英文全名+性別+年齡+學生/在職+手提+電郵+過去參加過或者打算未來參加的英文考證+考證目的<br />\n<br />\n電郵至：westricego@gmail.com"},{"pid":"1383854fd85e87b749fde660534b821c000c4b73","tid":809641,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:43:01.000Z","msg":"幫幫手啦"},{"pid":"d82414d35defd15bd536349018b4b64d2fd87dbd","tid":809641,"uid":191405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T11:05:49.000Z","msg":"已sd email"},{"pid":"77b234fe8b80df5966fc572dd67a65451b2aeae3","tid":809641,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T11:07:45.000Z","msg":"樓主食水咁深 <br />\n上次做有百五㗎喎"},{"pid":"972961b9d027824e0d9979f2b269f4d4cd89a250","tid":809641,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T11:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主食水咁深 <br />\n上次做有百五㗎喎</blockquote><br />\n你有百五既，我forward晒d info畀你。我收你$20一個得啦。你畀$130參加者啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請你留電郵。"},{"pid":"0bcc2d146c97348b3aa98cd9d481c8f3a53b1604","tid":809641,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375980121de22a6d2c8eeb86955887ef346eb2f0","tid":809641,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c